WEBVTT - English subtitles

00:06.050 --> 00:10.320
A team of brilliant scientists united in secrecy to build the first atomic bomb.

00:10.320 --> 00:15.040
The remote Los Alamos compound became the center of America's most secret WWII project.

00:15.040 --> 00:19.350
Inside the laboratories, researchers pushed physics into a new era.

00:19.350 --> 00:24.020
Engineers constructed The Gadget, the first plutonium implosion device ever built.

00:24.020 --> 00:28.060
On July 16, 1945, Oppenheimer unleashed the world's first nuclear explosion.